All Our Favorite Hot Springs

On this page you can find all the hot springs that we've been to and documented across Idaho, Oregon, Utah, and beyond. All the hot springs we've listed are well-known and we work hard to not spoil any local secret spots, as those have to be earned with sweat, tears, and maybe some sick burns.
